Description: MOTRA Default installation target for basic device setup 
 MOTRA Playbook Default provides a list of tools typically required for working with the MOTRA images and setups for the companion repository MOdular Testbed for Researching Attacks. This package provides a meta package to get all the required tools to get started.
 .
 MOTRA also provides: motra, motra-networking, motra-database, motra-hacking
 Currently shipped tools are: vim, git, tree, jq, python3, htop, btop, wget, curl, ca-certificates, tmux, less, man, openssl, openssh-client, psmisc, tldr
